\c 114
\s Simba raJehovha parwendo rwavaIsiraeri
\p
\v 1 Pakubuda kwaIsiraeri Imba yaJakobho ichibuda pakati pavanhu vakanga vanorumwe rurimi;
\v 2 Judha akaitwa imba yake tsvene, Nalsiraeri ushe hwake.
\v 3 Gungwa rakazviona, rikatiza; Jorodhani rwakadzokera shure.
\v 4 Makomo akapembera samakondobwe, Nezvikomo samakwayana.
\v 5 Unonzweiko iwe gungwa, zvaunotiza iwe? Newe Jorodhani, zvaunodzokera shure?
\v 6 nemwi makomo, zvamunopembera samakondobwe; nemwi zvikomo, samakwayana?
\v 7 Bvunda iwe pasi, pamberi paShe, Pamberi paMwari waJakobho;
\v 8 Iye akashandura dombo, rikava dziva remvura,
